      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by (product_id) (rate(mwa_product_orders_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{product_id}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "초당 처리된 구매 건수 — 상품(sku)별, 최근 5분 평균",
